To run this code you first need to pull this repo by doing git clone into your local. You must have java 1.8 or higher version. 
Open intellij IDE and go to file in intellij and open folder(name of foler is matrix-sum-calc).
Select main directory and open com.matrix.calc package.
Open Main.java class.
Right click on Main.java class and run 'Main.main()' and you will see an answer.




